

     
      "Ah, yes, the sad case of Uriel.  He'd been an archangel....but he was perhaps a bit overly zealous in the execution of his duties...slew all the creatures of myth.  Dragons, everything.  He was -- recalled -- in 700 and some odd."  He thinks for a few minutes.  "No, I can honestly say that I can recall no times when one of those recalled was not recorded immediately.  And there have been very few of those even."  "The sad truth is, Saint Ivan has disappeared!"
     
    
